overview: Murano Store is specialized in wholesale and retail items in Murano glass, especially in lighting, complements for the furnishing of interiors, objects and gift items, jewelry and high quality glass . All items are made by our glass masters using the ancient techniques of Murano glass. The products are certified and guaranteed with Murano Store brand synonymous with quality and reliability at the same time, professionalism and courtesy. While ensuring competitive prices and strict selection of top quality products. Solutions for your business, Murano Store is able to provide solutions for contract. Murano Store also works with interior designers, architects and interior designers. Our special glassware is required for special applications for hotels, restaurants, shops, offices, banks, boats, airports. Our long tradition at your service to create, produce and sell pieces on request.
